Does your #UPPAbabyVISTA need some TLC after all of your winter strolls ? Our Tune-UP Gear-UP Expert, Sam Osborne has all of the tips and tricks clean your VISTA wheels and keep you strolling smoothly all winter long!❄️ Tip: volume up!🔊
 
Looking for more info to help at-home Tune-UP's? Connect directly with our Tech Experts and schedule your virtual Tune-UP Gear-UP at the link in bio today!

node.text:
✨FEATURE FRIDAY✨ Planning a fun summer getaway? Pack your #UPPAbabyVISTA and hit the road! Want to learn our recommendations on the best way to easily fold, carry, and store your stroller into your vehicle? Check out this video to learn more!
 
1. Activate brake
2. Extend handlebar to the highest position
3. Recline seat to 2nd most upright position, forward-facing position
4. Pull up on two release triggers and rotate handlebar to ground

node.text:
This July, we’re going Behind the Brand with Naomi Vu, Creative Director here at @uppababy. For 11 years, Naomi has been driving the aesthetic and creative strategy, leading the talented in-house design team to execute the UPPAbaby vision and voice in all materials printed and published. Naomi also works with the Marketing and Product teams to communicate the visual identity and standards of the brand! When asked where she sees the brand in 10 years, Naomi says, “We will continue to be known for our Customer Experience, and the high quality and innovation of our products to meet the needs of all parents."
 
Fun facts about Naomi:
▪️Her family grew by welcoming their adorable baby girl two weeks ago 🎀 making her son a big brother!
▪️Skydiving is on her bucket list!

node.text:
FEATURE FRIDAY✨ Perfect for that independent older toddler who thinks they are too cool to stroll 😉, easily attach the PiggyBack ride along board to the back of your VISTA stroller. With a 55 lb weight limit and non-skid surface to prevent slipping, it’s the perfect accessory to stroll with three!

To attach:
1️⃣ Activate stroller brake.
2️⃣ Rotate attachment clips to face outward.
3️⃣ Position attachment clips to the inside of the frame above the rear wheel.
4️⃣ Slide attachment clips down onto the bracket until you hear an audible click.
 
Bonus! You can fold your VISTA with the PiggyBack attached!

node.text:
✨FEATURE FRIDAY✨ Mid-July, hello sun!☀️😎 Protect your little one from the sun’s rays with the MESA Cabana Accessory. The Cabana has UPF protection and a wind/rain protection layer that easily folds out over your infant car seat for unexpected weather while on your strolls. Check out the end of the video to learn how to fold the accessory to store in your stroller’s basket!
 
❗️Important❗️This product is intended for strolling and transporting a child outdoors only. The Cabana must be removed from the MESA carrier while riding in a vehicle.
